Package org.keycloak.models.cache

Interface UserCache.Streams

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Provider, UserBulkUpdateProvider, UserCache, UserLookupProvider, UserLookupProvider.Streams, UserProvider, UserProvider.Streams, UserQueryProvider, UserQueryProvider.Streams, UserRegistrationProvider
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    UserCacheSession
    Enclosing interface:
    UserCache
    public static interface UserCache.Streams
extends UserCache, UserProvider.Streams
    The UserCache.Streams interface differs from UserCache in that it extends the UserProvider.Streams interface, allowing implementations of UserCache to focus on the Stream-based methods in the UserProvider interface.
